1 G. 1. The Governor shall appoint the chair for an initial term
2 of three (3) years. At the end of the chair's initial three-year
3 term, and every two (2) years thereafter, members of the Council
4 shall elect, by a majority vote, a new chair.
5 2. Council members shall serve no longer than three (3) years,
